         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480"><!-- p2l3-r11 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Hd1e108">Rubrica 11</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De acquirendis amicis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e114">
              <pb ed="#V" n="41-v"/>
              <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
      ¶ De acqurendis amicis. Rubrica. 11
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/><ref>ISocrates in exhorta
      <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>tionibus. c
      <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Qd1e127">Neminem amicum concilies priusquam
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>perttenes quo pacto se gesserit er
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>ga priscos amicos: credas enim etiam erga te
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>huiusmodi futurum cuiusmodi erga illos fuit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e137">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>
               ¶ <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. i. e. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Qd1e141">Omnia cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>amico delibera: sed de ipso prius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e148"> /
      <ref>Idem de
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>remediis fortuitorum. e. 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Qd1e150">Ibi amicum queras
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>vbi inuenias: quere inter liberales artes: inter
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>recta et honesta officia: quere in laboribus ad men
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>sam: ista res non queritur: quere aliquem frugi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e162">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>
               ¶ <ref>Lucanus li. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Qd1e166">Cole felices: miseros fuge.
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>Aduersis non deesse decet: sed leta secutos:
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>Nulla fides vnquam miseros eligit amicos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e174">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>
               ¶ <ref>Marcialis cocus li. vndique suscepto. c. 3.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Qd1e178">Sepe diuque suo quem dignum censet amore.
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>Pertractat sapiens: sic amat ex habitu.
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>Antequaem ames erisippe proba: sed amare probatum
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>Cura: totoque illum pectore suscipias.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-d1e190">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
               ¶ <ref>Cato. c. 5. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31480-Qd1e194">Cum tibi vel socium: vel fidum queris amicum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>Non tibi fortuna est hominis: sed vita petenda.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
